products.title: Valencia Parchment Roller Blind
products.metadescription: If you're looking for something gentle and simple in colour but want to keep away from whites and creams, this valencia parchment roller blind will be an excellent choice.   This light, sandy coloured blind will provide a pale contrast to your room that will effortlessly blend in

products.title: Valencia Simplicity Beige Roller Blind
products.metadescription:
This valencia simplicity roller blind is light beige; think of an extremely milky coffee. Some might say buff or ecru, whatever you call it, it's a very nice neutral shade that adds just enough colour to the window.   
This colourway is beautiful in both modern settings and home
